quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  78,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  78,1,yeh log kis cheez ke baray mein pooch gach kar rahay hain ?
  78,2,kya uss barri khabar ke baray mein
  78,3,jis ke mutaliq yeh mukhtalif chay magoyan (khusar phusar) karne mein lagey huway hain ?
  78,4,"hargiz nahi, anqareeb aِnhin maloom ho jaayegaa"
  78,5,"haan, hargiz nahi, anqareeb aِnhin maloom ho jaye ga"
  78,6,kya yeh waqea nahi hai ke hum ne zameen ko farsh banaya
  78,7,aur pahoron ko menkhon ki terhan garh diya
  78,8,aur tumhe ( Mardon aur aurton ke ) joron ki shakal mein peda kya
  78,9,aur tumhari neend ko baais sukoon banaya
  78,10,aur raat ko parda posh
  78,11,aur din ko muaash ka waqt banaya
  78,12,aur tumahray oopar saat mazboot aasman qaim kiye
  78,13,aur aik nihayat roshan aur garam chairag peda kya
  78,14,aur baadalon se lagataar barish brsayi
  78,15,taakay is ke zareya se ghalla aur sabzi
  78,16,aur ghany baagh agayin ?
  78,17,be shak faislay ka din aik muqarrar waqt hai
  78,18,"jis roz soor mein phoonk maar di jaye gi, tum fouj Dur fouj nikal aao ge"
  78,19,aur aasman khol diya jaye ga hatta ke woh darwazay hi darwazay ban kar reh jaye ga
  78,20,aur pahar chalaye jayen ge yahan taq ke woh saraab ho jayen ge
  78,21,dar haqeeqat jahannum aik ghaat hai
  78,22,sarkashon ka thikana
  78,23,jis mein woh muddaton parre rahen ge
  78,24,uss ke andar kisi thandak aur peenay ke qabil kisi cheez ka maza woh nah chakhain ge
  78,25,kuch miley ga to bas garam pani aur zakhamo ka dhowan
  78,26,( unn ke krtoton ) ka bharpoor badla
  78,27,woh kisi hisaab ki tawaqqa nah rakhtay thay
  78,28,aur hamari ayaat ko unhon ne bilkul jhutla diya tha
  78,29,aur haal yeh tha ke hum ne har cheez gun gun kar likh rakhi thi
  78,30,"ab chako maza, hum tumahray liye azaab ke siwa kisi cheez mein hargiz izafah nah karen ge"
  78,31,yaqeenan Muttaqiyun ke liye kaamrani ka aik maqam hai
  78,32,baagh aur angoor
  78,33,aur no khaiz hum sun larkiyan
  78,34,aur chalakte hue jaam
  78,35,wahan koi laghu aur jhooti baat woh nah sunen ge
  78,36,jaza aur kaafi inaam tumahray Rab ki taraf se
  78,37,uss nihayat meharban khuda ki taraf se jo zameen aur asmano ka aur un ke darmain ki har cheez ka maalik hai jis ke samnay kisi ko bolnay ka yaara nahi
  78,38,"jis roz rooh aur mulaika saf basta kharray hunge, koi nah bolay ga siwaye uss ke jisay rehman ijazat day aur jo theek baat kahe"
  78,39,"woh din barhaq hai, ab jis ka jee chahay apne Rab ki taraf palatnay ka rasta ikhtiyar kar le"
  78,40,"hum ne tum logon ko uss azaab se dara diya hai jo qareeb aa laga hai jis roz aadmi woh sab kuch dekh le ga jo is ke hathon ne agay bheja hai, aur kafir pukaar utthay ga ke kash mein khaak hota"
